description:
Atomic Robo lands on the front lines of World War II against the science freaks and devastating weird weaponry of Nazi Germany - from invincible walking tanks to atomic-powered weather cannons to the Monster Soldiers of the Third Reich. Can ROBO and Ther Sparrow, Britain's greatest covert operative, complete their mission and turn the tide of the war without killing one another?

Collects Atomic Robo: Dogs Of War #1-5.
name: Volume Two

volume.name: Atomic Robo and the Dogs of War

description:
It is 1926 when H.P. Lovecraft comes calling to warn Atomic Robo of imminent doom. But the Shadow From Beyond Time escapes into the future, intersecting with our world through the 20th century! The future and history of the universe hangs in the balance as Atomic Robo teams up with, uh, Atomic Robo in a last-ditch effort to protect reality itself!

Collects Atomic Robo and the Shadow from Beyond Time #1-5.
name: Volume Three

volume.name: Atomic Robo and the Shadow from Beyond Time

description:
Manga Contents

  • Kinnikuman Nisei: Kykyoku no Chjin Tag Hen

1930's: A young ATOMIC ROBO yearns for adventure and excitement beyond the lessons of his creator, Nikola Tesla. Meanwhile, a mad scientist's quest for immortality puts the entire island of Manhattan in danger! It's up to ROBO's forbidden moonlighting team-up with vigilante gunfighter / incredibly reluctant mentor JACK TAROT to put a stop to it. Features a man with two skulls, a massive behemoth robot, vampires (a little) and first love.

Collects Atomic Robo and the Deadly Art of Science #1-5
name: Volume Five

volume.name: Atomic Robo and the Deadly Art of Science
